---
import HomeLayout from '../../layouts/HomeLayout.astro';
---

<HomeLayout title="About - Switch-Lit">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome to Switch-Lit.</h1>
      <p>
        We're thrilled to meet you here – at the beginning of an extraordinary journey into 
        the evolution of collaborative fiction as a catalytic structure for our time.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mission-block">
        <h2>Our mission is universal:</h2>
        <p>
          to manifest the collective imagination of creative writers and literary artists 
          through the connective power of collaborative fiction, poetry, and prose.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="vision-block">
        <p>
          We envision Switch-Lit as an infinite space in a remote corner of the Internet where 
          the forces of your imagination can freely meet and connect with other writers towards 
          the creation of new worlds, unimaginable by a single mind.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-block">
        <p>
          As we open this universe and community to all, we hope that you, dear Reader, will 
          become one of its first writers. How far and wide can you take a story worth sharing 
          (and with whom)? Where might it take all of us in the end?
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="team-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>TEAM</h2>
      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-member">
          <h3>KENNETH CHU</h3>
          <p class="location">Portland, OR (USA)</p>
          <p class="role">Founder & Managing Editor</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <h3>DIANA ECKER</h3>
          <p class="location">Portland, OR (USA)</p>
          <p class="role">Founding Editor</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <h3>JULIA KOSLOVSKAIA</h3>
          <p class="location">Berlin (DE)</p>
          <p class="role">Contributing Library Editor</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <h3>STUDIO AIRPORT</h3>
          <p class="location">Utrecht (NL)</p>
          <p class="role">Art Direction & Design</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <h3>SEPTEMBER DIGITAL</h3>
          <p class="location">Utrecht (NL)</p>
          <p class="role">Web Development</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <h3>ROB EN ROBIN</h3>
          <p class="location">Breda (NL)</p>
          <p class="role">Illustrations</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</HomeLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--spacing-xxl) 0 var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .content-section {
    padding: 0 0 var(--spacing-xxl);
  }

  .mission-block,
  .vision-block,
  .cta-block {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .mission-block h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .content-section p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .team-section {
    padding: 0 0 var(--spacing-xxl);
    background-color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .team-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .team-member {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .team-member h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .team-member .location {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .team-member .role {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .team-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
